{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/h1.png?t=1738142913\" />Interact with objects, handles, buttons, and wheels on each side. Crack enigmas and collect hidden puzzle tiles on a random side of the boxes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/1.gif?t=1738142913\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/h2.png?t=1738142913\" />You won't be able to compare reality with fiction!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/h3.png?t=1738142913\" />Once you unlock all 8 boxes of a Level Pack, you can compose a puzzle and discover a brief history of an invention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/h4.png?t=1738142913\" />It's not always easy to escape the room, so use all your IQ to crack the riddles. There's a logic behind all of them, even where it seems it's not!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/2.gif?t=1738142913\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/h5.png?t=1738142913\" />Play the game with your headphones to get immersed in this amazing adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/h6.png?t=1738142913\" />Got stuck on some enigma? No worries, you can still get a helpful hint! You can also get in touch with me in case you really can't make it through a riddle, I'll be glad to help ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/h7.png?t=1738142913\" />Available in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>*The game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/xslogo2.png?t=1738142913\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of\u00a0 <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Metal Box","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2738770/7b2e7bec2700b2399d1bf973f043cfb59d268033.jpg"},{"name":"Velvet Box","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2738770/c7968a978834505aff2c4b11308888fc895a22e7.jpg"},{"name":"Black Box","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2738770/6bea76b5a0ef72d988ef9cb4a5051f5334aae851.jpg"},{"name":"Pearl Box","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/imag